ь их лояльность и мотивацию. Психология, идеи, ошибки и практические советы для HR.\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/podarki-sotrudnikam-loyalnost\\\",\\\"image\\\":\\\"/images/blog/podarki-sotrudnikam-loyalnost-header.png\\\",\\\"datePublished\\\":\\\"2026-03-05\\\",\\\"dateModified\\\":\\\"2026-03-05\\\",\\\"author\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Graver.uz\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz\\\"},\\\"publisher\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Graver.uz\\\",\\\"logo\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ImageObject\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\\\"}},\\\"mainEntityOfPage\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"WebPage\\\",\\\"@id\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/podarki-sotrudnikam-loyalnost\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"script\",\"1\",{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Graver.uz\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Блог\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Подарки сотрудникам: как повысить лояльность\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://graver-studio.uz/ru/blog/podarki-sotrudnikam-loyalnost\\\"}]}\"}}]],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"nav\",null,{\"aria-label\":\"breadcrumb\",\"className\":\"mb-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"href\":\"/ru\",\"className\":\"hover:text-teal-500\",\"children\":\"Graver.uz\"}]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600\",\"children\":\"/\"}],[\"$\"